This is a rare opportunity. The existing tenant is vacating at the end of June 2016, leaving behind an extensive fit out that would be ideal for another medical use or other large space users such as education.
The owner is very realistic and will consider all reasonable offers.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Large Ground Floor Suite - Ideal for Medical uses or Education

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
First time on the market for over ten years
696sqm ground floor tenancy fronting Nerang Street. Previous use was a radiology clinic therefore the existing fit out includes an extensive number of examination rooms, change rooms, wash hand basins, procedure rooms, staff rooms, multiple toilets, large reception and waiting area.
The space ideally lends itself to another medical use, however under the Southport area plan, Education is another approved use.

Only 20 meters to the Southport Light Rail Station, China Town on the doorstep and a short walk to Australia Fair, Banks, Courts and Post Office.

The owner is keen to let this space ASAP and has is very market aware. So don't miss this rare opportunity .
